    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-12-09T22:25:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1950-12-09T22:25:00-05:00" n="1018"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1018">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">357.AD/12–950: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The United States Representative at the United Nations</hi>
                        (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Austin</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <gloss target="#t_niact1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">niact</hi>
                        </gloss>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New York</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1950-12-09T22:25:00-05:00"
                            >December 9, 1950—10:25 p. m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received December 9—10:31 p. m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_Delga1">Delga</gloss> 402. From Gross. Re Asian draft Korean
                    peace plan. Re <gloss target="#t_Gadel1">Gadel</gloss> 174, December 9,<note
                        n="1" xml:id="d1018fn1">See footnote 1 to telegram <gloss target="#t_Delga1"
                            >Delga</gloss> 397 received at 5:45 p. m. on December 9, <ref
                            target="#pg_1490">p. 1490</ref>.</note> when Lopez had been informed in
                    sense of reftel earlier this evening, he agreed not to take any action on basis
                    this or similar proposal without prior consultation and is so informing Romulo
                    who will return NY Monday. [Gross.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Austin</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
